### 🥗 Project Showcase: NutriScope
NutriScope is a client-side nutritional tracking engine that dynamically calculates biometric targets and tracks micronutrient risks in real-time. 

#### ⚙️ Core Engine Features
* **🧬 Dynamic Biometric Profiling:** Calculates basal metabolic rate (BMR) and daily macro targets (Protein, Carbs, Fats) based on age, weight, height, and specific activity multipliers (Mifflin-St Jeor equation).
